OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Organization SSA_PriceChDoc_CopyToOrg Selector Ref
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from Organization e where @additional_filters_notorg@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Area type
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: SELECT e.id FROM SCR_Combo_Item e WHERE e.comboCategory.id=@ssa_sales_area_type@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_Invoice Contract Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.project.id=@inpcProjectId@ and e.businessPartner.id=@inpcBpartnerId@ and e.salesTransaction=true and e.documentStatus='CO' and e.sCOSpecialDocType in('SCOARINVOICE','SCOARTICKET') and not exists(select 1 from SSA_Contract_Payment_Sched ps where ps.invoice.id=e.id and ps.sSAProjpropContract.id<>@inpssaProjpropContractId@)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_DebitMemo Contract Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.project.id=@inpcProjectId@ and e.businessPartner.id=@inpcBpartnerId@ and e.salesTransaction=true and e.documentStatus='CO' and e.sCOSpecialDocType in('SCOARDEBITMEMO')

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Invoice Prepayment SO Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "e.transactionDocument.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpemSsaPreorderdoctypeId') + "\' and e.documentStatus=\'CO\' and e.reinvoice=false and e.businessPartner.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcBpartnerId') + "\' and e.currency.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpcCurrencyId') + "\'"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_AD_User SalesRep
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as name from ADUser e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_ClientSalesCategory
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from SCR_Combo_Item e where e.comboCategory.searchKey='categoriaVentaCliente' and @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Payment Cond. Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from FinancialMgmtPaymentTerm e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Prospect Project Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from Project e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product All Non Generic Product Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.active=true and e.summaryLevel != true and e.isGeneric = false

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: AD_User Employee Selector Ref
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id,e.name as completename from ADUser e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Order Type Combo Item Selector Ref
SSA_ProspectOrContractProperty Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.project.id=@inpcProjectId@ and exists(select 1 from SSA_ProjProp_Contract_Line cl where cl.sSAProjectProperty.id=e.id and cl.sSAProjpropContract.id=@inpssaProjpropContractId@)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_Paymentoutfol_Li Internal Doc by BP Selector Reference
SSA_CreditMemo Contract Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.WHERECLAUSE: e.project.id=@inpcProjectId@ and e.businessPartner.id=@inpcBpartnerId@ and e.salesTransaction=true and e.documentStatus='CO' and e.sCOSpecialDocType in('SCOARCREDITMEMO','SCOARINVOICERETURNMAT') and not exists(select 1 from SSA_Contract_Payment_Sched ps where ps.invoice.id=e.id and ps.sSAProjpropContract.id<>@inpssaProjpropContractId@)

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SSA_ClientBusinessCategory
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from SCR_Combo_Item e where e.comboCategory.searchKey='categoriaRubroCliente' and @additional_filters@ and e.active=true
